OL,3,CHow algae on our railways could
OL,4,Ccapture 400x more carbon than trees
OL,6,FA pioneering project in Northumberland
OL,7,Fis investigating whether algae could
OL,8,Fprovide part of the solution to
OL,9,Fclimate change.
OL,11,FAlgae is being grown in a trial at
OL,12,FBerwick railway station.
OL,14,F"Algae can be up to 400 times as
OL,15,Fefficient at capturing carbon as
OL,16,Fplants are, they basically capture
OL,17,Fcarbon faster than any plant that we
OL,18,Fknow of." said Dr Mate Ravasz, CEO of
OL,19,Fbio-tech start up company, Algacraft.
