OL,3,CHow algae on our railways could
OL,4,Ccapture 400x more carbon than trees
OL,6,F"After we've actually extracted the
OL,7,Falgae those algae have value, we can
OL,8,Fuse them as fertiliser, we can use
OL,9,Fthem as pigment, we can use them as
OL,10,Fall sorts of industrial applications."
OL,11,Fsaid Dr Vidmar. "That value might pay
OL,12,Ffor the investment in the technology
OL,13,Fitself. So what we're trying to build
OL,14,Fis not just a science case for how
OL,15,Fthis is done but also a business case
OL,16,Fthat this can scale very easily right
OL,17,Facross the country."
